      "title": "FUD FAQ | A Weekly Community Thread | Week 74",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "FUD FAQ | A Weekly Community Thread | Week 74"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/0*pNRKjnLp0-bu7WCq.jpeg",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Top Question of the Week"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "li",
          "value": "Why does anyone listen to what’s-his-face anymore?"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "🤔"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*ZbFMavM6jqCykVNdNrSzLw.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Most Common Repeat Question"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "li",
          "value": "What does image synthesis have to do with governance in web3?"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "While the full extent, of how governance methods will change throughout protocols and projects as image synthesis integrates its way into more and more of our lives, will remain to be seen, within the DIGITALAX ecosystem we’re moving full steam ahead— experimenting with a new set of governance proposals and curation orientated methodologies. You can read more about that in our latest update:"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Top Controversies"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "What failed FEI and almost all other “decentralised algo” stablecoins so far is that they haven’t solved the big question: Where does stability actually come from?"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "With the latest Maker drama, we’ll have to see whether they can do any better."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*YroagBuwe0k1TrRxpEYYow.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Silly Fails and Trolling"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "If it is true, is it really that surprising? And if it isn’t, you really have to wonder about what it says about where crypto and the world is at as a whole for that fact that we’re so ready to believe something like this."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "The last few years sure have eroded a whole lot of trust. It’s a shame that we don’t have more robust systems for trustless coordination… yet."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*2qTOWv4mYG6rWdhcN0LI5g.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*4lMfRjSi78GfIWlDzUi_6Q.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "View all FUD FAQ here."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "If you would like a question answered or contribute content to next weeks article please reach out through our DIGITALAX Discord server in #FUD-FAQ channel!"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "See More Across Our Official Channels;"
